About
-----

In the @{b}About@{ub} window you'll find something useful about the program
itself and the author:

   @{b}*@{ub} the version number as well as a notice, if you are a registered
     user.

   @{b}*@{ub} The copyright notice and the address of the author (incl.  email
     address(es)).

   @{b}*@{ub} Your name, address and the serial number if you are a registered
     user.


@EndNode

